<para xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  Ant was meant to be an extendable build tool which can be used for general 
  task automation, even outside of the Java world. Indeed, before the .NET
  clone (<quote>NAnt</quote>) was available, it was often used to automate
  the building of .NET applications. 
</para>

